        {
            "id": 6132370,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 榮科(4989)股價拉至漲停，漲停價33.0元，成交1,005張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)29日12:20上漲3元，股價漲停報33.0元，委買38張，成交1,005張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電解銅箔之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌23.18%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.14%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+967 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+262 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+705 張</li> <li>融資增減：-743 張</li> <li>融券增減：+3,548 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6132370",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 12:20:15",
            "source": "cnyes",
